OL,3,CMan jailed for 13 years for attempted
OL,4,Crape of 74-year-old woman in 1992
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 13 years
OL,7,Fafter a Police Cold Case Unit linked
OL,8,Fhim to an indecent assault and
OL,9,Fattempted rape of a 74yearold woman
OL,10,Fin Stockport from more than 30 years
OL,11,Fago.
OL,13,FAdvances in forensic science allowed
OL,14,Fevidence from 1992 to be reexamined,
OL,15,Fand 34 years on, it yielded a match.
OL,17,FAron Traynor, who's 56, and of London
OL,18,FRoad, Stockport, was sentenced at
OL,19,FManchester Crown Court on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
