FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778259959
OL,3,CMan jailed for 13 years for attempted
OL,4,Crape of 74-year-old woman in 1992
OL,6,FThe victim, who has since passed away,
OL,7,Fwas attacked by a stranger while
OL,8,Fwalking near her home. No suspect was
OL,9,Fidentified.
OL,11,FHowever in 2005, the Cold Case Unit
OL,12,Fcommissioned further forensic
OL,13,Fanalysis, producing a nearcomplete
OL,14,FDNA profile that was added to the
OL,15,FNational DNA Database.
OL,17,FA breakthrough came when a DNA sample
OL,18,Ftaken from Traynor following an
OL,19,Funrelated arrest for drink-driving in
OL,20,FAugust 2023 matched the profile
OL,21,Fdeveloped by the Cold Case Unit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
