PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778259959
OL,3,CMan jailed for 13 years for attempted
OL,4,Crape of 74-year-old woman in 1992
OL,6,FTraynor was arrested in October 2023.
OL,7,Fand a fiveday jury trial in March
OL,8,F2026 found him guilty on both charges.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Cheryl
OL,11,FHughes said: "Time is quite simply no
OL,12,Fbarrier to justice.
OL,26,@sD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
