OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778259959
OL,3,CMan jailed for 13 years for attempted
OL,4,Crape of 74-year-old woman in 1992
OL,6,F"Today's sentencing shows that we
OL,7,Fnever close investigations into
OL,8,Fserious violent or sexual offences.
OL,9,FDNA is crucial, but it's the
OL,10,Fpainstaking work of our officers -
OL,11,Frevisiting evidence, tracing
OL,12,Fwitnesses, and rebuilding the
OL,13,Finvestigative picture - that
OL,14,Fultimately brings offenders to justice.
OL,16,F"Offenders should be in no doubt that
OL,17,Fforensic science continues to advance,
OL,18,Fand every interaction they have with
OL,19,Fthe criminal justice system increases
OL,20,Fthe chance of their crimes being
OL,21,Funcovered.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
