FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778259959
OL,3,CMan jailed for 13 years for attempted
OL,4,Crape of 74-year-old woman in 1992
OL,6,F"I'd like to thank the victim's family
OL,7,Ffor their support and cooperation in
OL,8,Fthis case. Although the victim sadly
OL,9,Fhas not lived to see justice served, I
OL,10,Fhope this sentence gives her family a
OL,11,Fsense of peace that the offender has
OL,12,Fbeen held accountable."
OL,14,FA statement from the victim's son was
OL,15,Fread in court, describing the
OL,16,Fdevastating and lasting impact the
OL,17,Fattack had on his mother's confidence,
OL,18,Findependence and wellbeing. He said
OL,19,Fthe assault changed her life
OL,20,Fprofoundly and affected the whole
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@WO]
